

Orange Leaf Book Contents
=====================

This is the source code for the Orange Leaf Book contents. 

The Orange Leaf Book is under the wiki form it is meant for quick unorganized contributions and serves as a staging area for the Blue Leaf Book.
 
It is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-Non Commercial-Share Alike 3.0 license. I hope you
enjoy it, I hope it helps you understand and use the Haiku operating system.


Errata
=====================
If you see anything that is technically wrong or otherwise in need of correction,
please message me to inform me.


Translation
=====================
If you wish to translate the book, please clone the repository and put your translation into the appropriate subdirector (ie: 'it' for Italian and so forth) and send me (aldeck) a pull request.
